  "design_notes": "We designed this Hard chart to mirror the high-energy curve of the track. The intro starts with clean, sparse beats to let the player warm up, stepping up to zigzagging 8th-note streams in the first drop. A brief middle breakdown at bar 38 offers a stops_breather moment, preparing the feet for the dense jumpstream peak of the second drop starting at bar 48, which features heavy sustain holds and moderate crossover flows. The chart resolves with simple, sparse taps into the outro, ensuring continuous engagement without any artificial pauses.",
